  "texts": [
    "AI systems have achieved high accuracy and fluency for straightforward language but struggle to replicate the art and essence of literature.",
    "The challenges align with findings from academic research on NMT creative deficiencies (Gaspari et al., 2015).",
    "Literal resemblance does not equate to expert literary translation.At their current capability, AI systems function more as diction-driven word converters rather than exploring expression possibilities in the target language.",
    "They lack integration of linguistic stylings beyond basics of grammar and vocabulary.",
    "Modeling the patterns, subjectivity, and cultural allusions inherent in literary language remains difficult (Eco, 2001)."
  ],
